race.description: Skin Fitness Hair And Beauty Provincial Handicap
race.comment: SUPER FREDS (9) tough gelding well graded here with the 3kg claim. Went out fast before tiring late when third over 1000m at Muswellbrook. Not far behind Bremel two-back and gets his chance. MR ROCK IT (1) comes to hand quickly and finds an easier test with the claim. Chipped away late on resumption when fourth over 1000m at Kembla Grange. Best form is over this trip and gets the right run. TRUMPER (5) well bred gelding who swept down the outside when resuming for a tough maiden win over 900m at Newcastle. Strips fitter and will appreciate the good tempo. LADY ZODIAC (6) lone victory came at this track and trip and returns with the two trials. Having her first run for the Fabio Martino yard and likely to go back from the sticky gate. Keep safe. KEV'S GIRL (11) tough mare holding her form. Winkers go on and has slim place prospects.
